<li><a href="/wiki/White_Magic_(Alice_A._Bailey)" title="White Magic (Alice A. Bailey)" class="mw-redirect">White Magic (Alice A. Bailey)</a> - White Magic adepts said to be able to spiritually travel to the etheric city of Shambala.</li>
