<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> Das, Sarat Chandra (1882). <i>Contributions on the Religion and History of Tibet</i>. First published in: <i>Journal of the Asiatic Society of Bengal</i>, Vol. LI. Reprint: Manjushri Publishing House, Delhi. 1970, pp. 81-82.</li>
